     <blockquote>
      <p>“This is where you start to get a hand on upper-level mathematics, but you are not killed with difficult problems. The theorems are accessible, and you learn to write proofs.”</p>
     </blockquote> 
     <p class="name"><strong>Gregory Hunt</strong> on Linear Algebra</p> 
